snippet.title: 【Original Genshin Fansong】 让风告诉你 (Let the Wind Tell You) Japanese Ver. By Nia Redalion
snippet.description:
[EN]
Lalala~

I tried to sing by imitating the voice of characters in Genshin Impact
There may be several different character voices. But I hope you can enjoy this song (o･ω･o)

[ID]
Lalalala~

Nia Mencoba bernyanyi dengan menirukan suara karakter di Genshin Impact
Mungkin akan ada beberapa karakter yang tidak mirip. tapi Nia harap kalian bisa menikmati lagu ini (o･ω･o)
